  <Docs>
    <summary>
            Indicates the type of capacity reservation. Allowed values are
            'Block' for block capacity reservations and 'Targeted'
            for reservations that enable a VM to consume a specific capacity
            reservation when a capacity reservation group is provided. The reservation
            type is immutable and cannot be changed after it is assigned.
            </summary>
